1
00:01:43,570 --> 00:01:45,850
Previously on Fairy Tail:

2
00:01:47,250 --> 00:01:48,420
Erza...

3
00:01:49,580 --> 00:01:50,870
I apologize.

4
00:01:51,170 --> 00:01:55,870
I'd forgotten one crucial thing...

5
00:01:59,210 --> 00:02:01,900
I am not protecting everyone!

6
00:02:01,900 --> 00:02:03,930
T-This is...

7
00:02:06,630 --> 00:02:13,340
It is I... who am always... being protected!

8
00:02:15,070 --> 00:02:18,050
Trust... Bonds...

9
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:22,530
Their true strength...

10
00:02:24,250 --> 00:02:26,070
It is not "One", but "Many"!

11
00:02:29,310 --> 00:02:30,830
What an amazing guild!

12
00:02:32,780 --> 00:02:33,790
Excellent.

13
00:03:04,890 --> 00:03:06,370
You...

14
00:03:06,370 --> 00:03:07,920
Your body...

15
00:03:15,310 --> 00:03:17,060
Frozen Spirit.

16
00:03:19,370 --> 00:03:20,360
You...

17
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,810
Your body...

18
00:03:22,890 --> 00:03:25,240
A side effect of the Lost Magic, you see.

19
00:03:26,300 --> 00:03:28,600
It seems I overused it considerably...

20
00:03:33,550 --> 00:03:35,190
I will keep my promise.

21
00:03:36,050 --> 00:03:38,300
Everyone's magic power 
will be returned to them.

22
00:03:42,220 --> 00:03:44,800
Do you know a man by the name of Jellal?

23
00:03:45,710 --> 00:03:46,490
Yes...

24
00:03:47,350 --> 00:03:52,660
He lost his mind after supposedly 
being possessed by the ghost of Zeref.

25
00:03:53,460 --> 00:03:56,460
A tragic man who traverses 
a life of nothingness.

26
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,640
He was someone you held dear?

27
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,840
My apologies.

28
00:04:11,110 --> 00:04:13,290
I believe that was all the work of Ultear.

29
00:04:14,520 --> 00:04:22,150
I heard it was an 8-year plan to have the Magic 
Council turn a blind eye to our actions at the time.

30
00:04:26,330 --> 00:04:28,240
She is a fearsome woman.

31
00:04:28,730 --> 00:04:32,330
Master Hades trusts her more than anyone.

32
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:36,430
Why are you so fixated 
on searching for Zeref?

33
00:04:40,320 --> 00:04:42,640
The magic at the beginning of the world...

34
00:04:43,820 --> 00:04:46,620
To get closer to the One Magic.

35
00:04:47,450 --> 00:04:48,180
...perhaps?

36
00:04:49,670 --> 00:04:51,520
The One Magic?

37
00:04:56,550 --> 00:04:59,360
And what happens when you get there?

38
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:05,700
Jellal dreamt of Heaven.

39
00:05:06,470 --> 00:05:07,650
We...

40
00:05:07,650 --> 00:05:08,600
Hey!

41
00:05:21,290 --> 00:05:23,220
The One Magic.

42
00:05:36,860 --> 00:05:37,890
What?

43
00:05:38,440 --> 00:05:40,430
Power is welling up within me!

44
00:05:40,430 --> 00:05:41,820
What's happening?

45
00:05:42,100 --> 00:05:44,000
My body is filling with magic power.

46
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,560
It's coming back!

47
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:46,370
Yes!

48
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:49,570
Yeah, it's back.

49
00:05:50,330 --> 00:05:53,230
Our power is back!

50
00:05:58,020 --> 00:05:59,110
Okay!

51
00:05:59,110 --> 00:06:00,330
Back in business!

52
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:04,130
Go, my babies!

53
00:06:11,140 --> 00:06:12,790
What happened, I wonder?

54
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:16,180
Anyway, it seems like our 
magic power is back to normal.

55
00:06:16,180 --> 00:06:21,150
Maybe Carla and the others are late 
getting here because of what happened?

56
00:06:21,150 --> 00:06:23,350
What happened, Azuma?

57
00:06:23,350 --> 00:06:26,030
Their magic power is back to normal!

58
00:06:38,500 --> 00:06:41,880
With even Gildarts here 
losing his magic power...

59
00:06:42,370 --> 00:06:44,750
He's not even a match for me...

60
00:06:47,900 --> 00:06:49,300
You got your power back?

61
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:57,430
As a proctor of this exam, it ain't 
dignified for me to take a beating like this.

62
00:06:57,960 --> 00:07:02,390
I gotta put on a good show 
in front of those kids!

63
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,990
Good!

64
00:07:12,940 --> 00:07:14,950
Good, Gildarts!

65
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:18,990
Let's have a fight where 
we can fly even higher!

66
00:07:19,660 --> 00:07:23,250
How about we fight seriously now?

67
00:07:27,500 --> 00:07:29,380
Black Hole!

68
00:07:34,720 --> 00:07:36,300
What the...

69
00:07:36,690 --> 00:07:41,190
An infinite gravity well 
that sucks in everything!

70
00:07:41,190 --> 00:07:43,140
Why, you...

71
00:07:43,140 --> 00:07:47,430
Fly! Fly!

72
00:07:47,430 --> 00:07:50,150
Come forth, Dimguil's Tower!

73
00:07:50,150 --> 00:07:56,270
Blast these foolish Fairies with all 
that sadness, and return them to dust!

74
00:07:59,990 --> 00:08:02,070
What is this?

75
00:08:02,070 --> 00:08:03,410
I can't move!

76
00:08:05,030 --> 00:08:06,260
Damn it!

77
00:08:06,260 --> 00:08:07,250
Even we are caught up!

78
00:08:10,210 --> 00:08:11,750
Crap...

79
00:08:11,750 --> 00:08:13,200
I don't have a choice.

80
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:15,900
I'll use my Figure Eyes.

81
00:08:15,900 --> 00:08:18,330
But it won't work on someone with glasses...

82
00:08:18,650 --> 00:08:19,560
Actually...

83
00:08:22,210 --> 00:08:25,080
There's a man I can count 
on with his eyes wide open!

84
00:08:25,780 --> 00:08:28,080
I'll be controlling you for a bit!

85
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:31,320
Do it!

86
00:08:39,780 --> 00:08:40,950
Countin' on you!

87
00:08:40,950 --> 00:08:41,540
What?

88
00:08:51,470 --> 00:08:52,800
The spell is broken!

89
00:08:53,910 --> 00:08:55,230
Fried!

90
00:08:56,550 --> 00:08:57,720
Please!

91
00:08:57,720 --> 00:08:58,220
Right!

92
00:09:13,820 --> 00:09:14,940
Cracks?

93
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:23,270
If you wanna fly so bad, how 
about I send you flying?

94
00:09:24,250 --> 00:09:26,700
You broke my spell to pieces?

95
00:09:26,700 --> 00:09:27,550
Eh?

96
00:09:28,740 --> 00:09:30,600
Fight for what's right!

97
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:32,280
The heavens!

98
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,880
Écriture of Darkness!

99
00:09:40,890 --> 00:09:42,020
Perish!

100
00:10:18,770 --> 00:10:21,220
Looks like your magic 
power is back to normal...

101
00:10:29,850 --> 00:10:32,220
Ul's... will?

102
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:36,690
You're free to believe me or not...

103
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:42,210
I'm taking Zeref and leaving this island.

104
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:46,700
You... defeat Hades.

105
00:10:49,070 --> 00:10:53,240
With Ul's spell, Iced Shell, you 
should be able to defeat him.

106
00:11:06,110 --> 00:11:07,120
Please...

107
00:11:09,110 --> 00:11:14,650
You're the only one who can carry 
out what Ul and I have wished for!

108
00:11:25,930 --> 00:11:28,300
Hurry, hurry!

109
00:11:28,300 --> 00:11:31,470
It's like that weakness from 
before was just some bad dream...

110
00:11:31,470 --> 00:11:35,270
Just 'cause things are a little easier, 
it's not like we're fully recovered...

111
00:11:35,270 --> 00:11:37,930
Natsu, don't you think 
you're going a little fast?

112
00:11:37,930 --> 00:11:41,100
We gotta! I have to think of Gramps here!

113
00:11:41,100 --> 00:11:45,430
And I won't know what's happened to everyone 
else unless we get back to the camp!

114
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:48,910
I... can't go on...

115
00:11:48,910 --> 00:11:51,930
I'm so hungry I can't walk!

116
00:11:51,930 --> 00:11:56,780
Look here, li'l kitty. You <i>do</i> understand the 
situation we're in when you said that, <i>right</i>?

117
00:11:56,780 --> 00:11:59,400
Like they say, care killed the cat.

118
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:02,000
Actually, I am hungry.

119
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:04,970
The only thing I ate was the 
fire from that God Slayer,

120
00:12:04,970 --> 00:12:07,160
and then I beat the crap out of him...

121
00:12:07,160 --> 00:12:12,680
Well, me too. Cana's heavier 
than you'd think...

122
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:17,550
Cana's unconscious, but that's 
still a terrible thing to say...

123
00:12:17,550 --> 00:12:20,170
See? It's not always me!

124
00:12:20,170 --> 00:12:22,060
Everyone, we're in trouble!

125
00:12:23,410 --> 00:12:26,580
I was curious, so I climbed way up high.

126
00:12:26,580 --> 00:12:31,500
The giant tree growing on the island 
has collapsed down to the roots!

127
00:12:34,190 --> 00:12:40,070
Then that means the felling of the tree was 
the cause of our magic power drying up?

128
00:12:40,630 --> 00:12:42,900
It is called the Tenrou Tree.

129
00:12:43,190 --> 00:12:46,090
I hear it gives divine protection 
to those in the guild.

130
00:12:46,090 --> 00:12:52,580
I dunno the details, but anyone who's got 
a Fairy Tail mark can't die or something.

131
00:12:52,580 --> 00:12:56,390
Then that's why all the 
injured people made it.

132
00:12:56,390 --> 00:13:00,160
But then, why did our magic power return?

133
00:13:00,160 --> 00:13:01,880
The tree is still toppled...

134
00:13:02,470 --> 00:13:05,340
We cannot relax yet.

135
00:13:05,340 --> 00:13:09,550
Then, we must stay on our guard 
while our magic power recovers...

136
00:13:21,950 --> 00:13:23,530
All right...

137
00:13:25,040 --> 00:13:25,950
Gray.

138
00:13:26,870 --> 00:13:30,450
I... will defeat Hades.

139
00:13:31,340 --> 00:13:34,200
Iced Shell requires the caster 
to give up their life...

140
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:36,210
I know.

141
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:43,590
I know full well!

142
00:13:46,590 --> 00:13:47,600
Thank you.

143
00:13:47,600 --> 00:13:48,590
Back off.

144
00:13:49,490 --> 00:13:53,030
This isn't for you, or for Ul.

145
00:13:53,710 --> 00:13:55,340
It's for the guild!

146
00:14:17,920 --> 00:14:20,820
W-What's happened?

147
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:22,170
Everyone...

148
00:14:26,050 --> 00:14:28,340
Even Gajeel and Mira-san?

149
00:14:28,340 --> 00:14:31,290
I'll use healing magic right away!

150
00:14:31,290 --> 00:14:32,010
Natsu.

151
00:14:32,780 --> 00:14:34,530
Lisanna, you're safe!

152
00:14:34,530 --> 00:14:36,470
Lisanna, thank goodness!

153
00:14:36,970 --> 00:14:39,380
I appreciate the offer, 
but look at how many...

154
00:14:39,380 --> 00:14:40,940
Don't push yourself, Wendy.

155
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:44,720
And look here... You've 
been using magic all day.

156
00:14:44,720 --> 00:14:46,570
You have to rest a little, or else...

157
00:14:46,570 --> 00:14:48,830
I agree!

158
00:14:48,830 --> 00:14:51,570
Lisanna, what happened?

159
00:14:52,350 --> 00:14:54,630
This guy attacked us here.

160
00:14:55,100 --> 00:15:00,410
After that, for some unknown reason, 
our magic power suddenly disappeared.

161
00:15:00,410 --> 00:15:04,830
It was a close call, but Fried 
and Bickslow fought for us.

162
00:15:05,370 --> 00:15:10,920
But even before that, everyone had 
already been injured here and there...

163
00:15:11,570 --> 00:15:15,760
It's gotten so dire without 
me even realizing it!

164
00:15:16,210 --> 00:15:18,510
Lisanna, don't cry.

165
00:15:18,510 --> 00:15:21,220
The cheerful characters like us can't cry!

166
00:15:22,140 --> 00:15:23,400
Happy...

167
00:15:23,930 --> 00:15:25,690
Y-Yeah...

168
00:15:26,990 --> 00:15:28,530
Unforgivable...

169
00:15:28,890 --> 00:15:30,960
Completely unforgivable...

170
00:15:31,450 --> 00:15:32,510
Natsu...

171
00:15:32,820 --> 00:15:34,030
Natsu-san.

172
00:15:34,390 --> 00:15:37,490
So even the Master and Cana are casualties...

173
00:15:37,490 --> 00:15:39,950
What the hell's goin' on here?

174
00:15:39,950 --> 00:15:43,680
The Grimoire Heart battleship 
is anchored off to the east.

175
00:15:43,680 --> 00:15:47,960
Considering we need to defend this camp, 
how about splitting into two teams?

176
00:15:48,430 --> 00:15:51,420
One attack team, and one defense team?

177
00:16:09,280 --> 00:16:10,540
Meldy...

178
00:16:11,220 --> 00:16:14,280
Ul... Ultear...

179
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:18,120
Is that him?

180
00:16:18,120 --> 00:16:19,380
Yes...

181
00:16:20,150 --> 00:16:21,620
This is Zeref.

182
00:16:24,070 --> 00:16:25,630
Change of plans.

183
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:27,380
We're leaving this island like this.

184
00:16:27,380 --> 00:16:31,760
B-But, I haven't found Gray yet.

185
00:16:31,760 --> 00:16:34,280
Forget about him.

186
00:16:36,060 --> 00:16:38,300
He's not our enemy.

187
00:16:40,030 --> 00:16:43,600
What does Zeref have to do with Ul's wishes?

188
00:16:44,290 --> 00:16:45,870
Listen to me, Gray.

189
00:16:47,240 --> 00:16:51,070
My father was killed by Hades.

190
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:58,660
In order to get revenge, Ul chased 
after Grimoire Heart behind the scenes.

191
00:17:01,730 --> 00:17:06,620
After Ul's death, I found her 
diary and learned the truth.

192
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:10,670
In order to get revenge, I 
infiltrated Grimoire Heart.

193
00:17:14,250 --> 00:17:18,070
But, Hades's magic power was 
beyond anything I could imagine.

194
00:17:18,310 --> 00:17:22,040
Ul knew this, which is why 
she mastered Iced Shell.

195
00:17:23,940 --> 00:17:25,520
Iced Shell?

196
00:17:26,550 --> 00:17:29,030
I wasn't able to master it.

197
00:17:29,940 --> 00:17:32,520
Even though Ul's blood 
runs through my veins...

198
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:39,640
The only magic I know of right now 
that can defeat Hades is Iced Shell.

199
00:17:45,950 --> 00:17:48,040
Don't worry about Zeref.

200
00:17:48,620 --> 00:17:50,900
I will seal him away, outside this island,

201
00:17:50,900 --> 00:17:53,900
so that no one will ever find him again.

202
00:17:55,220 --> 00:17:57,300
I'm not handing him over to Hades!

203
00:18:01,050 --> 00:18:07,550
Please, you're the only one who can 
carry out what Ul and I have wished for!

204
00:18:14,360 --> 00:18:16,280
He isn't our enemy.

205
00:18:18,430 --> 00:18:19,280
He's a pawn!

206
00:18:23,160 --> 00:18:27,490
He actually bought that story 
I came up with on the spot?

207
00:18:27,490 --> 00:18:29,230
Seriously?

208
00:18:31,940 --> 00:18:36,430
If this goes well, then Hades 
and Gray will off each other!

209
00:18:36,430 --> 00:18:39,250
I couldn't think of anything better!

210
00:18:39,540 --> 00:18:41,140
Even Master Hades?

211
00:18:41,140 --> 00:18:42,300
But, why?

212
00:18:42,900 --> 00:18:47,020
Zeref will be ours alone!

213
00:18:47,710 --> 00:18:50,730
You're going to trick Master Hades?

214
00:18:51,200 --> 00:18:56,930
Gray, Hades... Everyone should just 
dance in the palm of my hand...

215
00:18:56,930 --> 00:18:59,630
I'm not handing Zeref over to anyone!

216
00:18:59,630 --> 00:19:01,660
He's mine, all mine!

217
00:19:04,250 --> 00:19:05,640
Oh, pardon me...

218
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:11,330
I really shouldn't put so 
much confidence in Gray.

219
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:16,630
But he should at least 
serve to distract Hades.

220
00:19:19,660 --> 00:19:22,460
Let's leave the island before he catches on.

221
00:19:22,460 --> 00:19:23,200
Right.

222
00:19:26,430 --> 00:19:28,370
Who's this woman?

223
00:19:28,370 --> 00:19:29,410
Juvia.

224
00:19:30,030 --> 00:19:31,330
She and Gray are close.

225
00:19:39,820 --> 00:19:41,310
What are you doing?

226
00:19:41,310 --> 00:19:43,240
I'm going to kill her, obviously.

227
00:19:44,140 --> 00:19:47,250
But, she can't fight any more...

228
00:19:47,250 --> 00:19:48,190
Stay quiet.

229
00:19:49,300 --> 00:19:52,290
I won't let Gray have 
even a hint of a future.

230
00:19:52,970 --> 00:19:56,790
He will be destroyed by Hades, 
or die from Iced Shell.

231
00:19:57,140 --> 00:20:01,800
Or even if you manage to survive, 
you'll have lost your precious friend!

232
00:20:25,070 --> 00:20:26,360
Gray!

233
00:20:28,690 --> 00:20:30,870
I thought as much.

234
00:20:31,330 --> 00:20:33,620
Oh, I'm surprised.

235
00:20:33,920 --> 00:20:35,580
When did you catch on?

236
00:20:36,070 --> 00:20:39,460
I never believed a damn thing you said!

237
00:20:39,460 --> 00:20:41,240
I see.

238
00:20:41,240 --> 00:20:45,470
So, you pretended to believe me in 
order to find out my true aim...

239
00:20:46,040 --> 00:20:47,250
You naughty boy.

240
00:20:47,250 --> 00:20:51,470
I've decided never to use that magic again!

241
00:20:54,140 --> 00:20:57,020
I stopped you before 'cause 
I didn't want you to die.

242
00:20:57,750 --> 00:21:00,020
Maybe I didn't get through to you?

243
00:21:02,300 --> 00:21:05,280
No matter what Ul wanted...

244
00:21:05,760 --> 00:21:08,430
I have my own will!

245
00:21:08,430 --> 00:21:11,740
I'm going to continue living, 
along with my friends!

246
00:21:12,990 --> 00:21:14,230
Live...

247
00:21:15,400 --> 00:21:20,040
Sheesh... I guess you're not 
such a good boy after all.

248
00:21:21,010 --> 00:21:23,870
I had hoped you'd get lucky 
and get rid of Hades for me...

249
00:21:25,150 --> 00:21:29,950
Honestly, I really didn't want to fight you.

250
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:36,270
After all, you're one of that 
woman's beloved pupils...

251
00:21:41,260 --> 00:21:45,150
You've chosen the most painful 
way to die, you know!

252
00:21:45,770 --> 00:21:47,650
Bring it on, rotten daughter!

253
00:21:48,220 --> 00:21:51,660
I'm gonna teach you a lesson 
in your mother's place!

254
00:21:52,180 --> 00:21:53,790
About that...

255
00:21:54,160 --> 00:21:57,250
You've made one big mistake.

256
00:21:58,750 --> 00:22:02,710
I am the leader of the 7 Kin of Purgatory!

257
00:22:03,620 --> 00:22:06,480
You don't stand a chance against me!

258
00:23:55,430 --> 00:23:57,220
All right!

259
00:23:57,220 --> 00:23:59,170
We've beaten all the 
enemies around for now...

260
00:23:59,170 --> 00:24:00,900
Time to take on the bossman!

261
00:24:00,900 --> 00:24:05,270
Sorry to kill your buzz, but you 
hardly show up next episode.

262
00:24:05,270 --> 00:24:06,240
What?!

263
00:24:06,240 --> 00:24:08,780
The main character doesn't 
show up? I can't believe it!

264
00:24:08,780 --> 00:24:11,540
